{"image_id": "MPC_2013_page_120", "image_size": [1259, 1646], "ocr": [{"text": "100", "bbox": [614.6, 1566.2, 645.9, 1589.2]}, {"text": "Derivatives Designated as Fair Value Accounting Hedges", "bbox": [96.6, 85.1, 588.0, 108.2]}, {"text": "In 2012, we terminated interest rate swap agreements with a notional amount of $500 million that had been entered into as fair", "bbox": [96.6, 120.5, 1156.6, 143.6]}, {"text": "value accounting hedges on our 3.50 percent senior notes due in March 2016. There was a $20 million gain on the termination", "bbox": [96.6, 145.6, 1154.5, 168.6]}, {"text": "of the transactions, which has been accounted for as an adjustment to our long-term debt balance. The gain is being amortized", "bbox": [96.6, 170.6, 1151.6, 193.6]}, {"text": "over the remaining life of the 3.50 percent senior notes, which reduces our interest expense. The interest rate swaps had no", "bbox": [96.6, 195.6, 1124.3, 218.6]}, {"text": "accounting hedge ineffectiveness.", "bbox": [96.6, 220.6, 378.1, 243.7]}, {"text": "The following table summarizes the pretax effect of derivative instruments designated as accounting hedges of fair value in our", "bbox": [96.6, 256.0, 1163.2, 279.1]}, {"text": "consolidated statements of income:", "bbox": [96.6, 281.0, 390.1, 304.1]}, {"text": "Gain (Loss)", "bbox": [906.0, 343.2, 1005.0, 366.3]}, {"text": "(In millions)", "bbox": [102.8, 374.4, 206.5, 397.4]}, {"text": "Income Statement Location", "bbox": [315.5, 374.4, 545.9, 397.5]}, {"text": "2013", "bbox": [788.7, 374.4, 830.4, 397.5]}, {"text": "2012", "bbox": [934.6, 374.4, 976.3, 397.5]}, {"text": "2011", "bbox": [1080.9, 374.4, 1122.6, 397.5]}, {"text": "Derivative", "bbox": [102.8, 403.8, 190.8, 426.9]}, {"text": "Interest rate", "bbox": [115.3, 435.1, 214.3, 458.2]}, {"text": "Net interest and other financial income (costs)", "bbox": [315.5, 437.0, 701.0, 460.0]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [753.3, 437.0, 763.7, 460.0]}, {"text": "—", "bbox": [844.3, 437.0, 865.1, 460.0]}, {"text"